nt offers a dramatic and cautionary tale about what can happen when secret police power goes unchecked.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCivil rights workersxBiographyxAlabama. 0aCivil rights workerszAlabamavBiography. 0aInformersxBiographyxAlabama. 0aInformerszAlabamavBiography. 0aMurderxAlabamaxLowndes County. 0aMurderzAlabamazLowndes County. 0aUndercover operationsxAlabama. 0aUndercover operationszAlabama. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030012999140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300129991423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300129991/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles